title: Meet and Greet with Writer, Producer and Comedian
desc: MEET AND GREET     Comedian/Producer/Writer   Camille Solari    Camille has written, performed and produced television and films for Comedy Central, Lifetime Television, Universal Pictures, Nickelodeon, The Weinstein Company, HBO, Oxygen Network, and many more.
